* **CSS Transitions:** [MDN Web Docs on Transitions](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/transition)
* **Flexbox Layout:** [CSS-Tricks Guide to Flexbox](https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/)


